
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Limited_Liability";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<style>
    body {
        background-image: url('../Content/images/llp.jpg');
        position: auto;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        width: 100%;
    }
</style>

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="offset-7 col-5 mt-5 mb-2">
            <form class="form" action="/Home/Enquiry" method="post">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
                        <div class="text-center" style="font-size:25px; color:aliceblue;">REQUEST A CALL BACK</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="name"><b></b></label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="txtname" name="txtname" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="email"><B></B></label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="txtemail" name="txtemail" placeholder="Email Address" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="num"><B></B></label>
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon bg-light p-1">+91 </span>
                                <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="txtnumber" name="txtnumber" placeholder="Please Enter Number.." required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg float-right">Get Start</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="bg-light card">
        <h3 class="card-header  text-center  bg-info text-white">
            LIMITED-LIABILITY PARTNERSHIP
        </h3>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-justify">
                Limited Liability Partnership (LLP) firm is a new form of business entity established by an Act of the
                Parliament. LLP has the feature of Company and partnership firm also. LLP in India is governed by the
                Limited Liability Partnership Act 2008. LLP allows members to retain flexibility of ownership (similar to
                Partnership Firm) but provides a liability protection. The maximum liability of each partner in an LLP is
                limited to the extent of his/her investment in the firm. An LLP has its owner Permanent Account Number
                (PAN) and legal status. LLP does not get terminated by the death or insolvency of the limited partners.
                We need two or more persons for incorporation of LLP that will be associated for carrying on a lawful
                business with a view to profit shall subscribe their names to an incorporation document.
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <div class="bg-light card">
        <div class="card-header  bg-info text-white">
            <h2 class="text-left">Process:</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="text-black-50" style="font-size:20px;">
                <ol start="1">
                    <li> Obtaining DSC and DIN</li>
                    <li>Application for Name Approval</li>
                    <li>LLP Agreement</li>
                    <li>Filing of LLP form on MCA Portal</li>
                    <li>LLP Incorporation Certificate</li>
                    <li> Apply for PAN & TAN & Bank Account</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <br>
    <br>


    <div class="bg-light card">
        <div class="card-header  bg-info text-white">
            <h2 class="text-left"> Documents (Required for Registration)</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="text-justify">
                <ol start="1">
                    <li> Copy of PAN Card or Passport (Foreign Nationals & NRIs)</li>
                    <li>Copy of Voter's ID/Passport/Driver's License</li>
                    <li>Copy of Latest Bank Statement/Telephone or Mobile Bill/Electricity or Gas Bill</li>
                    <li>Passport-sized photographPassport-sized photograph</li>
                    <li>Specimen signature (blank document with signature [partners only]</li>
                    <li>Copy of Latest Bank Statement/Telephone or Mobile Bill/Electricity or Gas Bill</li>
                    <li>Copy of Notarised Rental Agreement in English</li>
                    <li>Copy of No-objection Certificate from property owner</li>
                    <li>Copy of Sale Deed/Property Deed in English (in case of owned property)</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

